{"tid":1746773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選唔重要？唔好再比藉口自己輸啦","createTime":"2019-11-23T02:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:24:10.000Z","uid":38991,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b0474799b5500cf6d87c476f2aa2fcd93f14d922","tid":1746773,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:04:28.000Z","msg":"大量吹風怪揾藉口比自己輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知係咪想為選舉吹淡風等少d人出黎投票<br />\n<br />\n1.區選唔係公投<br />\n2.唔信體制內抗爭<br />\n3.對家會種票/換票箱<br />\n4.政府明知輸點會比你投<br />\n<br />\n全部都係廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我同你講，無論港共點卑鄙點出古惑，我地都要贏呢場區選</span>，好簡單，萬一輸左，<br />\n<br />\n1.國際社會就會覺得你班香港人係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來都唔係咁多人支持，失去動力同道德力量去幫你<br />\n<br />\n2.港共/奶共派/藍屍會更強硬，爭取五大訴求只會越黎越困難<br />\n<br />\n我地唯一可以做，一定要做就係贏呢場選舉，唔只要過半，要大勝！淨返一日時間盡量影響身邊既人去投票，唔係係到吹淡風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02539aab1a4db2513ffcd2d2d657702155584ec2","tid":1746773,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"即刻沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f193e08f1fe6c2637c8c0013589aaec8f05fba8e","tid":1746773,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:06:56.000Z","msg":"唔投票/投白票/投廢票=多謝支持獨裁暴政"},{"pid":"82b092c0b0d30dd744af625ebcecc7c21b07ef19","tid":1746773,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:10:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f0bae516eed3f17f46fae3d4c03280b7806770f","tid":1746773,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce2024c8f4ee8b307ca679dd09c0ed73a0d890d","tid":1746773,"uid":265271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b0474799b5500cf6d87c476f2aa2fc